        "contentHtml": "\n<p class=\"summary-text\"><b>At Tigo Colombia, we improved the digital UX across product, service, and self-service experiences.</b>\nWe redesigned key journeys—package activation, top-ups, and plan migrations—reducing friction, unifying the experience, and delivering measurable results, guided by Atomic Design principles and a refreshed look &amp; feel.View prototipe:\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/lRrvRtAFM0Fjx6kT1S94xZ/Tigo-store-CO?page-id=17388%3A28525&amp;node-id=17388-28875&amp;viewport=-507%2C233%2C0.11&amp;t=diRkAoqsKcEE5XiD-1&amp;scaling=scale-down&amp;content-scaling=fixed&amp;starting-point-node-id=17388%3A28875&amp;show-proto-sidebar=1\" target=\"_blank\"> Web→ </a>\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/lRrvRtAFM0Fjx6kT1S94xZ/Tigo-store-CO?page-id=17388%3A41903&amp;node-id=18124-24141&amp;viewport=1187%2C95%2C0.26&amp;t=HXl4I3hKGvNv681X-1&amp;scaling=scale-down&amp;content-scaling=fixed&amp;starting-point-node-id=18124%3A24141&amp;show-proto-sidebar=1\" target=\"_blank\"> Mobile→ </a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-1 post-img\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"images/blog/single/com-co-02.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<br/>\n<h3>Challenge</h3>\n<p>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">An oversized hero reduced scanability.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Key actions weren’t visible above the fold.<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n<h3>Solution</h3>\n<p>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Task-first, modular layouts with core actions visible from the first fold.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Micro-interactions and persistent navigation to improve clarity and speed.<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n<h3>Impact</h3>\n<p>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">2X traffic to the mobile category<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">+36K activations<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">–28% abandonment<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n<h3>Role &amp; Approach</h3>\n<p>\n<class=\"post-date\">As a UX Strategist and Lead Designer:<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Reduced friction through heuristic-driven, task-first layouts.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Improved clarity and feedback with modular design and micro-interactions.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Standardized persistent navigation across platforms to speed up key actions.<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n",
        "fullHtml": "\n<div class=\"row\">\n<article class=\"post\">\n<div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-1 post-img\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"images/blog/single/com-co.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-8 offset-md-2\">\n<h1 class=\"post-title mar-top-50\">Discovery Tigo CO</h1>\n<ul class=\"post-meta\">\n<li class=\"post-category\">Category - <a href=\"#\">UX &amp; Product Redesign<a href=\"#\"></a></a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"post-content-wrap\">\n<p class=\"summary-text\"><b>At Tigo Colombia, we improved the digital UX across product, service, and self-service experiences.</b>\nWe redesigned key journeys—package activation, top-ups, and plan migrations—reducing friction, unifying the experience, and delivering measurable results, guided by Atomic Design principles and a refreshed look &amp; feel.View prototipe:\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/lRrvRtAFM0Fjx6kT1S94xZ/Tigo-store-CO?page-id=17388%3A28525&amp;node-id=17388-28875&amp;viewport=-507%2C233%2C0.11&amp;t=diRkAoqsKcEE5XiD-1&amp;scaling=scale-down&amp;content-scaling=fixed&amp;starting-point-node-id=17388%3A28875&amp;show-proto-sidebar=1\" target=\"_blank\"> Web→ </a>\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"https://www.figma.com/proto/lRrvRtAFM0Fjx6kT1S94xZ/Tigo-store-CO?page-id=17388%3A41903&amp;node-id=18124-24141&amp;viewport=1187%2C95%2C0.26&amp;t=HXl4I3hKGvNv681X-1&amp;scaling=scale-down&amp;content-scaling=fixed&amp;starting-point-node-id=18124%3A24141&amp;show-proto-sidebar=1\" target=\"_blank\"> Mobile→ </a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"col-md-10 offset-md-1 post-img\">\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"images/blog/single/com-co-02.jpg\"/>\n</div>\n<br/>\n<h3>Challenge</h3>\n<p>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">An oversized hero reduced scanability.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Key actions weren’t visible above the fold.<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n<h3>Solution</h3>\n<p>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Task-first, modular layouts with core actions visible from the first fold.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Micro-interactions and persistent navigation to improve clarity and speed.<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n<h3>Impact</h3>\n<p>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">2X traffic to the mobile category<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">+36K activations<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">–28% abandonment<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n<h3>Role &amp; Approach</h3>\n<p>\n<class=\"post-date\">As a UX Strategist and Lead Designer:<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Reduced friction through heuristic-driven, task-first layouts.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Improved clarity and feedback with modular design and micro-interactions.<br/>\n                                    • <class=\"post-date\">Standardized persistent navigation across platforms to speed up key actions.<br/>\n</class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></class=\"post-date\"></p>\n</div>\n</div></article>\n</div>\n<ul class=\"post-nav clearfix\">\n<li class=\"post-prev\">\n<a href=\"case-engage-scale-personalize-book.html\">\n<span>Previous Case</span>\n<h4>Engage · Scale · Personalize — Book</h4>\n</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"post-next\">\n<a href=\"case-tigo-buy-phone-plan-redesign.html\">\n<span>Next Case</span>\n<h4>Buy a Phone + Plan</h4>\n</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n",
