        "image": "/images/portfolio/stacked-fullwidth/img_1.jpg",
        "meta": [
            "<strong>Client:</strong> UNE / TIGO&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Year:</strong> 2015 / 2016&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Category:</strong> Smart TV&nbsp;&nbsp; Art Direction / IU."
        ],
        "contentHtml": `
            <p class="summary-text">
            The new UNE channel was the result of a collaborative effort to redefine
            the TV viewing experience on Smart TV platforms.
            </p>

            <p>
            Working closely with UNE's animation team and programming directors, we
            designed the channel's interface from the ground up. Inspired by Google's
            Material Design principles, the goal was to bring clarity, movement, and
            consistency to a traditionally static TV environment.
            </p>

            <p>
            The result was a completely redesigned channel interface that combined fluid
            animations and a coherent visual language.
            </p>

            <p>
            This approach transformed the channel into a complete digital experience: 
            modern and aligned with the evolving expectations of TV platform users.
            By combining strong art direction, meticulous interaction design, and close collaboration between teams, 
            the new UNE channel laid the foundation for more complete and engaging Smart TV experiences.
            </p>
        `,
